Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:13.93,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞  玩偶裝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.35,0:02:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說綾音那裡也被偷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:19.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是放在櫥櫃裡的飯團
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小偷跑進神社裡會遭天遣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島上會出現小偷  真少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.84,0:02:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近谷類和蔬菜  好像都被偷了好幾棵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.56,0:02:31.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺有點不安心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  究竟是誰做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.75,0:02:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人  今天還真早…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的臉上有什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便當…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.08,0:03:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這是熊熊的蜜罐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.26,0:03:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是姐姐大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我吃的  承蒙款待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就承認了?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.46,0:03:56.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  雖然飯團  水果  蜂蜜  饅頭是我吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:58.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他可不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道認為偷全村食物的小偷會是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.74,0:04:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人的平時的行為太差了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連行人大人都這樣看待我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.76,0:04:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會失落成這樣  就是說真的不是麻知姐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行蹤不明的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  行人大人一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:34.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在違抗姐姐大人的話會很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:42.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也不能放任小偷不管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.23,0:04:44.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  我們也幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.67,0:04:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那分頭找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在三天前被偷的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那被偷什麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:17.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  沒看到過這麼拼命的麻知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼麻煩的事情誰去做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會去的…樂意至極…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.55,0:05:31.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:39.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來被偷的很嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:44.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件從村子最北邊開始慢慢延伸到南邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後昨晚是海龍神社
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.15,0:05:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說  小偷盯上的下個地方會是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離這條線最近的家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.84,0:05:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大概會是香里家或者是雪乃家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:05:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  那麼今晚只要去監視的話也許就能抓住犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為分兩組的抽籤  不准互相抱怨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會又使詐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.83,0:06:14.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你先抽不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你乾杯  發光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和公子一起在夕陽…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情…那種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直玩到天亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝小鈴的機會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們去香里家了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:07:00.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之晚上不得不聚在一起守小偷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:05.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小偷會是怎麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這島上以前都沒有過這種壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行…行人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是小偷做的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些全部都吃掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明每天都只偷一家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天卻是海龍神社和黃瓜地兩家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以往推想的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小偷會來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人還沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家的時候常常開夜車的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知姐氣勢十足呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為被誣陷了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.12,0:08:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別睜著眼睡覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…就不會困了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此…彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:08:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  貓頭鷹…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:08:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.58,0:09:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一招
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然接住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼黑的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會讓你逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就揭穿你的真實面目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.97,0:09:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,束手就擒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.15,0:09:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我老實點…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭部脫出了?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被砍下的人頭?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭…被拽下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:09:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個頭套
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  為什麼是這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.52,0:10:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.53,0:10:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看守的話我一個人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.41,0:10:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:10:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.75,0:11:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很累
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先睡吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.84,0:11:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浴室裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人來  小鈴就待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了  小偷…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:13.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你認識的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見到的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:36.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…冷靜點…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.27,0:12:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簍筐?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像冷靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  為什麼要鑽進簍筐裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅長在別人面前露面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.45,0:13:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一家都在演雜技
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我從以前開始就很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舞台上一直失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了克服害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.14,0:13:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了獨自的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.46,0:13:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是和以前一樣無法和人交談
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避人眼目在旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能好好地交到朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這樣的我在途中也交到了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人開始一起旅行不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢用光了想坐船回國的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被暴風雨捲入…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒來的時候就發現漂流到這個島上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 也不用一一畫在紙上說明…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然每天都下決心…今天要出現在大家面前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又太害羞又猶豫起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  這樣就事件解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過偷東西可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…想讓你們分我點東西吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻開不了口…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心就…對不起了…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  黃瓜地的是不是太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.49,0:14:27.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  把田地全都吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不知道…那不是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:36.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是遠野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的人果然很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是說我也很奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃瓜地也許是你的朋友做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.88,0:14:59.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野先生非常喜歡黃瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.38,0:15:06.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那朋友也漂流到了這個島上太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.94,0:15:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知被嫁禍了不是很生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道梅梅是犯人  不知道會做出什麼事情來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.17,0:15:21.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先回家  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  麻知
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾音把這個給我 說是犯人似乎戴著這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紙糊的面具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅連這個都戴著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為太害羞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.12,0:15:48.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:53.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在追蹤這個氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到也是時間的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:15:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回是千影家的黃瓜地…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:11.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到這個程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.40,0:16:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道黃瓜小偷是誰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:24.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這氣味和剛才面具的是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧  氣味消失了 難道是錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在這種地方徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.03,0:16:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了嗎  被抓住就很糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  在我回這裡之前要老實待著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野先生…遠野先生是我重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…都兩人一起旅行著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.56,0:17:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到遠野先生就在附近  就坐立不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.94,0:17:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.35,0:17:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想快點見到朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.05,0:17:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…行人先生  非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  犬犬好像知道遠野先生在哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊  這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.05,0:17:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣味消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跳過去的話有點遠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:05.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過也沒有可以藏的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法騙過我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻知姐…聽我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.62,0:18:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道你是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.61,0:19:06.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我找的多幸苦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.53,0:19:08.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:10.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你不要亂跑亂動了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:16.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 乖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是河童嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫遠野先生一直以為是人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童什麼虛構動物根本不可能存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是烏龜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然嫁禍給我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.97,0:19:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:33.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然向我挑釁  真有勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…請等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.21,0:19:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷食物的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠野先生沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是真正的犯人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢陷害我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.61,0:19:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起…饒恕我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:19:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對做壞事的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要給予懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.31,0:20:04.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,stop
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:05.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.05,0:20:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也好好道歉了 就饒恕她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  麻知姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道理由  看起來不像是壞孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人誤會是大姐頭平時的行為不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經那麼道歉了  還懲罰的話那是魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺我才是壞人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.21,0:20:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然行人大人這樣說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.34,0:20:51.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏龜…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得平復下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.84,0:21:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你是從哪裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:16.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:23:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此島上增加了新的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.55,0:23:03.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.16,0:23:05.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅梅和遠野先生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:07.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是非常奇怪的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.98,0:23:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這島上的卻人也非常的和藹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.78,0:23:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許很快就會令人意外地融洽相處了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.36,0:23:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人…活該…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.07,0:23:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心情不好
